{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "希诺亚（夏日Ver.） 第4话 两位研究者",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "希诺亚前辈！好久不见了！\\n我都惊了！没想到这么巧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "你过得还好吗！？我听说\\n你现在住在一座城堡里！？\\n对了！那个实验怎么样了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "等、等一等，玛丽……\\n你一下问这么多问题……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "啊！抱歉！希诺亚前辈！\\n我太高兴了，忍不住就……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "那我一个个问……\\n为什么你会在这里？我听说\\n你现在住在迷雾森林的城堡里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "嗯……是的。我是住在那里。\\n今天我是和城里的伙伴们\\n一起来这里度假的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "我也一样！\\n是来度假的呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "因为新的实验成功了，\\n沙龙奖励了我旅费！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "度假就是好啊！\\n能放空脑袋尽情享受！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "下次我要挑战更高难度的实验！\\n感觉自己充满了斗志！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "这、这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "（无论是研究还是玩乐……\\n我都不如这孩子……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "希诺亚前辈？你怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "我是在感慨，\\n玛丽真了不起呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "我收到你写给我的信了。\\n听说你当上了学术顾问……\\n恭喜你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "那我就先告辞了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "诶！？希诺亚前辈！？\\n请等一下！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "不，我不等！\\n我和你已经没什么好说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "就算前辈没有，\\n但我还有话想说啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……\\n跑、跑不动了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "啊！？前辈，你还好吧！？\\n请到阴凉处休息一下……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "谢、谢谢……\\n呼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "我果然，不行呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "诶？希诺亚前辈？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "不管是研究还是玩乐……\\n我都完全比不上你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "甚至还给你添麻烦……\\n我们的立场\\n就像是反过来了一样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "前辈……真是的！\\n你在说些什么呀！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "没有前辈的悉心教导，\\n就没有今天的我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "我真的很感谢前辈！\\n我给你看的论文末尾……\\n就是最好的证明！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "你是说把我……\\n列在特别感谢名单里\\n那件事吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "的确……要把一个\\n被赶出沙龙的人的名字\\n登上去应该并不容易……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "你一定在很多人面前低声下气，\\n才换来了这个特许……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "这根本不算什么！\\n毕竟是为了我尊敬的\\n希诺亚前辈啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "诶？尊、尊敬！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "嗯！虽然在沙龙的时候\\n因为害羞而没能说出口……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "但作为一名研究者，\\n我打心眼里尊敬希诺亚前辈！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "诶！？我、我何德何能……\\n做实验也总是失败……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "现、现在也是！\\n时空之穴的实验\\n也一直都没能成功……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "但是……你并没有放弃\\n造出时空之穴这一目标吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "那当然！因为这个实验\\n就是我的一切啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "呵呵……我就是尊敬\\n你这种地方呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "创造时空之穴\\n是时空物理魔法的巅峰，\\n也是难度最高的实验……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "由于其内容实在不太现实，\\n几乎所有的研究者都只把它\\n当成一纸空谈，不放在眼里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "但是，希诺亚前辈不一样。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "通过理性思考与新颖的创意，\\n在一次次失败中改进实验方法……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "每次都会用满怀希望的表情\\n喊出“下次一定要成功！”……\\n那样的前辈非常耀眼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "我从前辈身上感受到了\\n对研究者来说最重要的东西，\\n那就是永不言弃的精神！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "是前辈教会了我这一点，\\n我对前辈的感激之情\\n真的无以言表！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "我作为一位研究者的起点……\\n就是与前辈\\n一起做实验的那段日子！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "玛丽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "我在实验成功前，\\n也失败了无数次……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "每当那时，我脑中就会浮现出前辈的身影，\\n然后继续努力。因为我知道\\n如果是前辈，绝对不会就这样放弃！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "啊……玛丽？你要去哪？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "嘿嘿。这些话\\n说出来还真有些害羞……\\n我差不多该走了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "最后……希诺亚前辈！\\n我会一直支持你的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120072_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛丽",
            "context": "前辈的话一定、绝对能！\\n做成前无古人的大实验！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "玛丽……我都不知道\\n那孩子居然是这样想的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "对研究者来说最重要的东西，\\n永不言弃的精神吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "没错！那一天，那一刻，\\n我不是已经下定决心\\n一定要造出时空之穴了吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "谢谢你，玛丽……\\n是你唤醒了我的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "你让我想起了\\n连我自己都快要遗忘的……\\n重要的事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110009_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希诺亚",
            "context": "以及，我的起点！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}